longBusinessSummary: Vmoto Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the manufacture and distribution of electric two-wheel vehicles worldwide. Its electric two-wheel vehicles include electric mopeds and motorcycles. The company offers its products primarily under the VMOTO, VMOTO Fleet, Super Soco, and E-Max brand names. Vmoto Limited was incorporated in 2001 and is based in Perth, Australia.
